document_data.name: Eel Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Eel Street''' was a major road in the asteroid city of [[Bral]].
document_data.Description: Eel Street began with an intersection with [[Lamp Street]] on the starboard side of the [[Rock of Bral|asteroid]] and ran to its port side at [[Anchor Street]], covering most of the width of the [[Bral/Low City|Low City]]. Along the way, it crossed [[Hammer Street]], [[Grand Street]], and [[Dragon Street]], for a total distance of roughly {{SI|1300|ft.|long=yes}}. It formed the trailing-edge borders of [[Giff-town]] and [[Shou-town (Bral)|Shou-town]].
